              "script": "\t# implement your handler here\n\tOperatorID \u003d payload[\u0027OperatorID\u0027]\n\tdata \u003d self.props.data\n\tfor i in data:\n\t\tif i[\u0027Action\u0027] \u003d\u003d 1:\n\t\t\tsystem.db.runNamedQuery(\"Project_VECV/Quality/updateDefectStatus\",{\"OperatorID\":OperatorID,\"ModifiedBy\":self.session.custom.loggedInUserId,\"TRN_StationDefect_Id\":i[\u0027TRN_StationDefect_Id\u0027]})\n\t\t\tstate \u003d \u0027Warning\u0027\n\t\t\tmessage \u003d (\"All defect Cleared\")\n\t\t\tProject_VECV.PopUp.Alerts.showAlert(str(state), str(state.capitalize()), str(message), \"true\", \"Okay\", \"\", \"\", \"\", \"\", \"closePopup\", \"closePopup\", \"closePopup\",\"\",\"\",\"\",\"\")\n\tself.refreshBinding(\u0027props.data\u0027)",
